WEBVTT

00:01:12.120 --> 00:01:13.359
Save me!

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:16.159
Save me! Save me!

00:01:16.319 --> 00:01:17.599
Li Ran, save me!

00:01:18.040 --> 00:01:19.040
Save me!

00:01:21.760 --> 00:01:22.480
Save me!

00:01:23.799 --> 00:01:24.879
Save... Save me!

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:26.000
Save me!

00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:42.760
There's no signal at all.

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:44.719
The flash flood must have affected the base station.

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:46.239
Since we're here, let's make the best of it.

00:01:46.760 --> 00:01:49.640
Look at Mr. Tan, truly a big businessman.

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:50.719
Calm as still water.

00:01:50.799 --> 00:01:51.400
Miss Li.

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:53.359
It's rare to have a quiet moment.

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:54.879
Let's enjoy the moment.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:56.400
Everyone is here.

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:57.439
I might as well mention something.

00:01:57.719 --> 00:01:59.519
Although the communication signal is cut off...

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:01.480
And we've lost contact with the outside world...

00:02:01.799 --> 00:02:03.079
But there's no need to worry.

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:05.319
The supplies here are very plentiful.

00:02:05.879 --> 00:02:07.120
Enough to last at least a month.

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:10.120
Who wants to stay here for a month?

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:12.520
Just waiting here for Lawyer Luo?

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:15.400
Speaking of which...

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.240
It's fate that we gathered here.

00:02:19.439 --> 00:02:20.000
Perhaps...

00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:21.280
We can chat about...

00:02:22.240 --> 00:02:24.039
Stories from the past with my sister and brother-in-law.

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:25.120
To mourn them.

00:02:27.759 --> 00:02:29.479
Since the will mentioned everyone...

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:30.240
It's a ghost.

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:32.080
Surely everyone has... with my sister and brother-in-law...

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.680
Some interesting stories, right?

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:36.680
Then I'll speak first.

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.159
I and the two deceased...

00:02:38.159 --> 00:02:38.800
Fine.

00:02:39.159 --> 00:02:41.360
I'd actually like to hear how every one of you...

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:45.240
Is exactly related to my brother and Difu.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:48.560
I'm a bit scared.

00:02:49.319 --> 00:02:51.240
I don't want to go back to my room alone.

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:53.879
Staying with you guys is fine.

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:57.039
In that case...

00:02:57.319 --> 00:02:58.639
Let's set a rule.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:00.280
If you want to hear others' stories...

00:03:00.919 --> 00:03:02.639
You have to tell your own story.

00:03:03.879 --> 00:03:05.479
It's only interesting if it's a two-way street.

00:03:05.759 --> 00:03:06.520
Detective Qi.

00:03:07.520 --> 00:03:08.240
You are an outsider.

00:03:08.520 --> 00:03:09.520
So may we trouble you...

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.319
To be a witness.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.919
Then I'll go first.

00:03:20.599 --> 00:03:21.719
Shui Ge, Shui Ge.

00:03:21.919 --> 00:03:24.159
Money, money, I... I will definitely pay it back.

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:24.919
Give me some time.

00:03:25.439 --> 00:03:28.120
Boss Fang, we are all businessmen.

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:29.080
We talk about integrity.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:30.840
You had trouble and asked me for money.

00:03:31.199 --> 00:03:31.800
I helped.

00:03:32.639 --> 00:03:34.479
When it's time to pay back, you say you have no money.

00:03:34.759 --> 00:03:36.080
Isn't that your fault?

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:38.439
Shui Ge, I beg you.

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:39.039
Don't be like this.

00:03:39.039 --> 00:03:39.520
Shui Ge, really.

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:40.159
No matter how much money...

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:41.479
I will definitely pay it back, Shui Ge.

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:44.879
You have no way.

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:46.439
I'll help you find a way.

00:03:47.479 --> 00:03:48.919
I'll take one today.

00:03:49.639 --> 00:03:50.000
Consider it interest.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.719
Shui Ge, no, no, Shui Ge!

00:03:56.319 --> 00:03:56.879
Scared?

00:03:58.479 --> 00:03:59.560
Shui Ge, Shui Ge.

00:04:00.039 --> 00:04:00.840
You... You...

00:04:01.199 --> 00:04:02.120
At most one week.

00:04:02.919 --> 00:04:03.479
Five days.

00:04:03.879 --> 00:04:04.520
Three days.

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:05.479
Okay, okay.

00:04:05.759 --> 00:04:07.439
If you don't pay up in three days...

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:08.639
You know what happens.

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:24.639
Lili.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:26.519
Fang Qiu, you jerk.

00:04:27.120 --> 00:04:28.160
You borrowed from loan sharks yourself...

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:29.399
To save your deadbeat dad.

00:04:29.399 --> 00:04:30.160
Don't drag me into this.

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:31.759
Lili.

00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:34.199
Can you just listen to me explain first?

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:36.920
From now on, I'm done with you.

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:38.279
If you want to die...

00:04:38.279 --> 00:04:38.879
Please die far away.

00:04:38.879 --> 00:04:39.279
Lili.

00:04:39.519 --> 00:04:39.920
Hello?

00:05:43.439 --> 00:05:43.959
Hello, Dad.

00:05:44.199 --> 00:05:45.120
I'm working overtime.

00:05:45.399 --> 00:05:46.360
You haven't eaten yet, right?

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:47.480
I'll go buy some for you.

00:05:53.160 --> 00:05:54.480
Sir, your takeout is ready.

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:55.680
The total is thirty-two.

00:05:56.839 --> 00:05:59.279
Money, it's always about money.

00:05:59.839 --> 00:06:02.519
Why does everyone come to me just to ask for...

00:06:14.240 --> 00:06:15.480
Sir, are you okay?

00:06:19.040 --> 00:06:19.759
I'm fine.

00:06:21.399 --> 00:06:22.360
You want the bill, right?

00:06:23.279 --> 00:06:23.680
Yes.

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:24.920
That'll be thirty-two.

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:27.079
Just give me thirty. I'll knock off the rest.

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:36.279
It's okay.

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:38.319
I... I often forget my wallet when I go out too.

00:06:39.319 --> 00:06:41.360
How about this meal is on me?

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:42.639
Let's be friends.

00:06:44.519 --> 00:06:45.319
Difu.

00:06:51.040 --> 00:06:52.160
Fang... Fang Qiu.

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:53.800
Then... then...

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:56.439
I'll definitely pay you back next time.

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:56.959
Okay.

00:06:57.399 --> 00:06:58.560
Please come again.

00:06:58.560 --> 00:06:59.079
Okay.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:01.000
Okay.

00:07:09.759 --> 00:07:11.040
Everything will get better.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:12.519
Hang in there.

00:07:17.959 --> 00:07:18.560
Bye-bye.

00:07:31.279 --> 00:07:32.160
At the lowest point of my life...

00:07:33.079 --> 00:07:33.920
Between life and death...

00:07:35.439 --> 00:07:36.480
Difu's appearance...

00:07:37.519 --> 00:07:39.759
Was like an angel sent by God to save me.

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:48.680
How did you end up owing loan sharks?

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:53.680
To pay for my dad's medical bills.

00:07:55.879 --> 00:07:56.839
He had cancer.

00:07:58.519 --> 00:08:01.439
My dad was like a mountain to me.

00:08:01.879 --> 00:08:02.639
After he got sick...

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:04.920
I was completely lost.

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:08.360
And with the loan sharks chasing me...

00:08:09.360 --> 00:08:11.240
I really just wanted to end it all back then.

00:08:14.439 --> 00:08:15.600
Three days are up.

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:16.680
Let me tell you...

00:08:17.399 --> 00:08:18.680
Even if you go to hell...

00:08:18.959 --> 00:08:20.279
I'll drag you back.

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:22.439
Shui Ge.

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:28.079
All I have left is my life.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:30.079
Take it.

00:08:38.879 --> 00:08:39.519
Stop!

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:46.639
This chick's not bad.

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:48.080
Difu.

00:08:48.759 --> 00:08:50.879
Shui Ge, Shui Ge.

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.000
Shui Ge.

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:52.840
Shui Ge.

00:08:53.759 --> 00:08:54.679
I'll pay you back the money.

00:08:55.720 --> 00:08:57.080
This has nothing to do with her.

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:59.879
How about she covers the interest for you first?

00:09:01.399 --> 00:09:01.879
Take her away.

00:09:02.279 --> 00:09:02.519
Don't!

00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:03.440
Hold on.

00:09:07.399 --> 00:09:08.840
Shui Ge, right?

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.080
You want to take me away?

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.320
You have to ask if I agree first.

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:14.559
So what do you want?

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:15.960
Holding a toy gun...

00:09:16.519 --> 00:09:17.360
Trying to scare me?

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:18.639
This is Taicheng.

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:21.840
Getting a toy gun is harder than getting a real one.

00:09:22.159 --> 00:09:23.600
Do you think I scare easily?

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:24.240
Try me.

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:35.600
Fang, consider yourself lucky.

00:09:36.720 --> 00:09:38.039
But the money you owe...

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:40.080
You still have to pay.

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:45.759
Here is a check for one million.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:47.799
Four hundred thousand is Mr. Fang's principal.

00:09:47.799 --> 00:09:49.240
Six hundred thousand is the interest.

00:09:49.639 --> 00:09:50.720
Consider this settled.

00:09:50.840 --> 00:09:51.639
Four million.

00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:53.519
And you're only paying one million?

00:09:53.519 --> 00:09:54.679
Do you take me for a fool?

00:09:54.919 --> 00:09:56.919
Look at who signed the check first.

00:10:02.559 --> 00:10:03.279
Is it enough?

00:10:04.279 --> 00:10:04.600
Enough.

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:08.279
Enough.

00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:12.159
More than enough.

00:10:14.639 --> 00:10:17.159
Our debt is settled.

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:20.240
From now on, we stay out of each other's way.

00:10:21.159 --> 00:10:21.639
Let's go.

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:35.039
Difu.

00:10:36.759 --> 00:10:37.600
Thank you.

00:10:39.039 --> 00:10:39.919
Now...

00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:42.240
You can start over.

00:10:58.440 --> 00:10:59.159
Fang Qiu

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:00.320
I'm leaving

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:06.679
I hope this money helps you through this crisis

00:11:08.039 --> 00:11:09.159
I am an unlucky person

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:11.200
I hope my departure

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:12.679
Will take your bad luck away too

00:11:14.519 --> 00:11:16.039
You are a very talented person

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:18.639
I believe you will succeed one day

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.320
I wish you a happy future

00:11:21.039 --> 00:11:21.639
Difu

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:25.159
Good

00:11:25.679 --> 00:11:26.799
That's a good story

00:11:27.039 --> 00:11:27.960
Melodramatic enough

00:11:31.279 --> 00:11:32.039
Darn it

00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:33.759
You cheating scum

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.120
I'll kill you for cuckolding my brother

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:37.759
You cheating scum

00:11:37.759 --> 00:11:38.559
Alright, alright

00:11:38.559 --> 00:11:39.679
Did you kill my brother?

00:11:39.679 --> 00:11:41.559
I didn't. Everything I said

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:43.919
Happened before Mr. Zhao and Difu

00:11:43.919 --> 00:11:44.679
Were together

00:11:49.399 --> 00:11:50.639
That's ancient history

00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:52.480
Why take it so seriously?

00:11:53.679 --> 00:11:54.720
Yeah, Ah Hai

00:11:55.360 --> 00:11:56.639
Your brother didn't care

00:11:56.639 --> 00:11:57.519
Why are you acting out?

00:12:00.919 --> 00:12:01.519
What was that noise?

00:12:04.960 --> 00:12:05.720
It's mine

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:08.480
I haven't seen my sister for years

00:12:08.879 --> 00:12:11.879
I wanted to learn more about her from your stories

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:13.279
So I recorded it

00:12:13.879 --> 00:12:14.919
Isn't that perfect?

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:17.759
What this kid just said is admissible evidence

00:12:17.759 --> 00:12:19.279
I... I don't care

00:12:19.480 --> 00:12:20.720
But Miss Li didn't

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:21.960
Get our consent to record

00:12:21.960 --> 00:12:23.360
Do you think that's appropriate?

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:25.840
I just wanted it as a keepsake

00:12:26.399 --> 00:12:27.679
If you all object

00:12:28.039 --> 00:12:29.159
Then I'll delete it

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:32.360
As a keepsake

00:12:33.559 --> 00:12:34.080
Miss Li

00:12:34.559 --> 00:12:35.879
You don't need to make excuses

00:12:37.679 --> 00:12:39.679
I have no objection if you want to investigate

00:12:39.960 --> 00:12:41.320
As long as you share the results

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:42.440
Of the investigation in the end

00:12:42.759 --> 00:12:44.240
I believe everyone here

00:12:44.759 --> 00:12:46.919
Thinks the Zhaos' deaths were suspicious

00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:48.639
And wants to know the truth

00:12:49.480 --> 00:12:50.759
I don't believe my sister committed suicide

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:53.360
If the Zhao couple was murdered

00:12:54.279 --> 00:12:55.399
Then the prime suspects

00:12:56.360 --> 00:12:57.639
Are us right here

00:12:57.639 --> 00:12:58.639
Because every one of us

00:12:58.639 --> 00:12:59.799
Is connected to the inheritance

00:13:01.279 --> 00:13:03.320
If they were really murdered

00:13:03.879 --> 00:13:05.960
I'm the one who should be ruled out first

00:13:08.639 --> 00:13:09.720
They were my benefactors

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:13.039
That check

00:13:13.519 --> 00:13:15.480
Was written to me by Mr. Zhao

00:13:15.960 --> 00:13:16.720
Hold on

00:13:17.720 --> 00:13:19.840
Look at who signed the check first

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:22.720
Also

00:13:23.279 --> 00:13:23.879
At that time

00:13:24.279 --> 00:13:25.720
For me to have any success

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:27.799
It was thanks to their help

00:13:27.799 --> 00:13:29.960
So I couldn't possibly have killed them

00:13:30.759 --> 00:13:31.679
You mean

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:34.039
Your tech company, right?

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:35.159
Right

00:13:36.360 --> 00:13:38.600
The next time I saw Miss Difu

00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:39.720
Was a year later

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:41.360
By then, she and Mr. Zhao

00:13:41.360 --> 00:13:42.639
Were already together

00:13:43.879 --> 00:13:45.159
I was online at the time

00:13:45.440 --> 00:13:47.399
Developing a social app

00:13:48.519 --> 00:13:50.639
And with Miss Difu's recommendation

00:13:50.639 --> 00:13:52.120
Mr. Zhao became my investor

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:55.360
So you hooked up with that stinking witch again

00:13:55.360 --> 00:13:56.320
Mr. Zhao Qihai

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:57.200
I'm warning you

00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:59.000
Mr. Zhao and Miss Difu

00:13:59.000 --> 00:14:00.360
Are the people I respect the most

00:14:00.799 --> 00:14:01.679
You can insult me

00:14:01.679 --> 00:14:02.519
You can beat me

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:03.879
But please respect them

00:14:16.159 --> 00:14:16.720
A Si

00:14:17.279 --> 00:14:18.080
Let me help you.

00:14:18.240 --> 00:14:19.320
No need, Miss Li.

00:14:19.759 --> 00:14:20.679
You are a guest.

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:22.320
It's fine.

00:14:22.919 --> 00:14:24.120
We're all trapped here.

00:14:24.519 --> 00:14:26.279
We should help each other.

00:14:26.720 --> 00:14:27.840
You are just like Madam.

00:14:28.399 --> 00:14:29.320
You're both good people.

00:14:30.919 --> 00:14:33.360
I haven't seen my sister in years.

00:14:33.639 --> 00:14:35.960
I don't know what she became like.

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:38.519
I often heard Madam mention you.

00:14:39.639 --> 00:14:41.720
I used to think it was strange too.

00:14:42.240 --> 00:14:43.720
Why you were sisters,

00:14:44.080 --> 00:14:45.279
yet never met.

00:14:45.519 --> 00:14:47.159
What matters is you, Miss Li Ran.

00:14:48.080 --> 00:14:49.759
You are the heir to hundreds of millions.

00:15:04.120 --> 00:15:04.919
So,

00:15:05.639 --> 00:15:07.440
I want to know more about my sister and brother-in-law.

00:15:09.559 --> 00:15:11.480
They were an angelic couple.

00:15:13.360 --> 00:15:15.480
Then how did you meet them?

00:15:16.320 --> 00:15:16.919
Yeah.

00:15:17.159 --> 00:15:17.879
Let's hear it.

00:15:18.799 --> 00:15:20.120
I've known Qishan for so long,

00:15:20.919 --> 00:15:22.279
but I've never heard

00:15:23.039 --> 00:15:25.120
that there was a scar-faced housekeeper at home.

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:29.759
Before I met them,

00:15:30.759 --> 00:15:32.440
I never dared to dream

00:15:34.639 --> 00:15:36.000
that one day I could actually

00:15:37.240 --> 00:15:38.759
live with such kind people.